Rating: 4
Easy go-to weeknight recipe. Can't believe other reviewers hated it...can only say that if you use fresh, never frozen fish it's a winner. I use fresh halibut in this recipe with extra garlic and follow the recipe otherwise. Sometimes add green beans if I have them. Or red onion. Point is, with so few ingredients you have to use good quality products because there's nothing to hide from. If you use frozen fish, it's going to taste like it. Add spice or peppers for a kick, like other reviewers. Be bold and enjoy!

